    "type": "mcq",
    "text": "The electric force between two charges is $F$. If both charges are doubled and the distance halved, the new force is:",
    "image": "",
    "options": [
      { "text": "$F$", "image": "" },
      { "text": "$4F$", "image": "" },
      { "text": "$8F$", "image": "" },
      { "text": "$16F$", "image": "" }
    ],
    "correct": 3,
    "explanation": "By Coulomb's law: $F = k\\frac{q_1 q_2}{r^2}$\n\nNew force: $F' = k\\frac{(2q_1)(2q_2)}{(r/2)^2} = k\\frac{4q_1q_2}{r^2/4} = 16F$"
